x = keras.layers.LSTM(150, return_sequences= True)(inputs)
x = keras.layers.Dropout(0.3)(x)

x = keras.layers.Dropout(0.3)(x)
x = keras.layers.LSTM(150)(x)
outputs = keras.layers.Dense(1, activation='linear')(x)
